                        <i class="fa-solid fa-bed-pulse fa-3x mb-3" style="color: #F38326;"></i>
                        <p class="mb-0">
                            Most countries significantly fall short of the 1:1000 doctor-to-patient ratio recommended by
                            the World Health Organization (WHO). Kenya for example, currently has a 1:17000 ratio with
                            huge gaps in health coverage. Mhealth4Africa’s Frontline Healthcare Champions are here to
                            work with public and private health institutions to expand health access.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
                    <div class="service-item bg-white text-center h-100 p-4 p-xl-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-doctor fa-3x mb-3" style="color: #F38326;"></i>
                        <p class="mb-3">
                            If you are looking to make a difference as a doctor, nurse, medical graduate, medical student, or community health worker, join us to expand healthcare delivery in your community. Let’s work together to make Universal Health Coverage a reality. Sign Up as a FRONTLINE HEALTHCARE CHAMPION TODAY!
                        </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-primary py-2 px-3" href="/signup">
                            Member Signup
                            <div class="d-inline-flex btn-sm-square bg-white text-primary rounded-circle ms-2">
                                <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
